<%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>

    <section class="hero bg-gray-800">
        <section class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-col">
            <div class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-row pb-0">
                <img src="/images/map.jpg" class="max-w-sm rounded-lg shadow-2xl" alt="Earth at night from space" />
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-snug">Professional Computer-Aided Dispatch Software</h1>
                    <p class="py-3">First Line Response is a tracking program designed for emergency management and
                        disaster response.</p>
                    <a href="/demo"><button class="btn btn-primary">View Demo</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <section class="hero-content flex-col lg:flex-col items-start pt-0">
                <p>In the emergency services field, telecommunicators utilize software called
                    computer-aided dispatch (CAD) to track 911 calls and first responders. Some of these systems are
                    extremely sophisticated, but their costs can be prohibitive for smaller
                    agencies who may find themselves literally limited to pen and paper. This is an issue because it
                    hurts response time and reliability.</p>
                <p>As an accessible CAD, First Line Response solves this problem while retaining the features essential
                    to keeping citizens and first responders safe.</p>
            </section>
        </section>


    </section>




