                    responders safe.</p>
                <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-xl lg:mx-auto">See what makes First Line Response different than the
                    competitors:</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
                <dl class="space-y-10 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-10 md:space-y-0">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <dt>
                            <div class="absolute flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary">
